@node Main "Ixo - Documentation"

                               'Ixo'  V1.0

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Ixo' is a @{" Workbench game " link play} where you place coloured bars in an
8 by 8 spaces game board. The idea is to create alignments of 8
horizontal bars in a row or 8 vertical bars in a column. If the
alignments have bars of the same colour and none of them are
crossing other bars, the better it is...

  However, watch out for the 'ClickoMeter', it counts the number of
moves you make... when it has reached its limit, the game is
over...

  Have fun!

